<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>لَيْسَ بِحَدِيثٍ وَكَذَلِكَ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٣١٣ - الْقِلَّةُ قَيْدُ الْفَرَاعِنَةِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَيَدُلُّ لِمَعْنَاهُمَا قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى <span class="c3">{كَلَاّ إِنَّ الإِنْسَانَ لَيَطْغَى أَن رّءَاهُ اسْتَغْنَى}</span> <span class="c4">[العلق: ٦ - ٧]</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٣١٤ - الْفَقْرُ فَخْرِي وَبِهِ أَفْتَخِرُ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>قَالَ ابْنُ حَجَرٍ مَوْضُوعٌ بَاطِلٌ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٣١٥ - فَمٌ سَاكِتٌ وَرَبٌّ كَافِي<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>لَيْسَ بِحَدِيثٍ وَكَذَلِكَ قَوْلُهُمْ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٣١٦ - اللَّهُ وَلِيُّ مَنْ سَكَتَ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٣١٧ - فِي آخِرِ الزَّمَانِ يَنْتَقِلُ بَرْدُ الرُّومِ إِلَى الشَّامِ وَبَرْدُ الشَّامِ إِلَى مِصْرَ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>قَالَ ابْنُ حَجَرٍ لَا أَصْلَ لَهُ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>